Joseph DIMATTEO, Libelant-Appellee, v. THE Steamship ESTRELLA, Her Engines, etc., Det Bergenske Dampskibselskab, Claimant-Appellant. Salvatore GRECO, Libelant-Appellee, v. Steamship ESTRELLA, Her Engines, etc., Det Bergenske Dampskibselskab, Claimant-Appellant. Nos. 32, 33. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Nov. 6, 1933. Hatch & Wolfe, of New York City (Carver W. Wolfe, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Paul Koch, of New York City, for appellee Dimatteo. Irving Spieler, of New York City, for appellee Greco.

Before MANTON, AUGUSTUS N. HAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decrees (2 P. Supp. 258) affirmed.
